title: Murder She Wrote Mystery Series
description:
MURDER, SHE WROTE is a series of original novels based upon the television series, Murder, She Wrote. Donald Bain writes them "in collaboration" with TV's most famous mystery writer, Jessica Fletcher of "Murder, She Wrote," who exists only as a fictitious character.
